I had let myself go.</i>

01:31:50.011 --> 01:31:52.046
<i>And while
I still struggle at times</i>

01:31:52.079 --> 01:31:54.648
<i>with the world
we live in today,</i>

01:31:54.682 --> 01:31:58.185
<i>you gave me something back
I was missing:</i>

01:31:58.219 --> 01:32:02.790
<i>The belief there is
still good in the world.</i>

01:32:07.695 --> 01:32:10.064
<i>I thank you for that, Jake.</i>

01:32:10.097 --> 01:32:13.167
<i>It's the greatest gift
a person could give.</i>

01:32:23.277 --> 01:32:24.779
Mom?

01:32:26.714 --> 01:32:28.049
You ready?

01:32:48.269 --> 01:32:50.738
<i>I didn't know about this one.</i>

01:32:53.007 --> 01:32:54.775
<i>It's outside the perimeter.</i>

01:32:56.310 --> 01:32:58.279
<i>Dad called this area
No Man's Land.</i>

01:33:13.761 --> 01:33:16.363
<i>I don't know how I feel
about luck these days.</i>

01:33:19.033 --> 01:33:20.835
<i>I know I'm prepared
for the worst</i>

01:33:20.868 --> 01:33:23.037
<i>if that should ever
actually happen.</i>

01:33:27.274 --> 01:33:28.609
<i>But really...</i>

01:33:30.744 --> 01:33:32.213
<i>I'm just hopeful.</i>

01:33:35.749 --> 01:33:37.384
<i>Hopeful for my future.</i>

01:33:40.788 --> 01:33:42.790
<i>Hopeful for this world.</i>

01:33:55.436 --> 01:33:57.037
Please be you.

